		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Makes sense. Using 8k mode is exactly what I need for this particular project. I guess I would want to change to 4kb if I wanted to easily animate some background graphics or something and leave the sprites alone. Maybe I will use 4kb anyway just so that will remain an option.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
