	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As far I know, the only point of using 8k mode is if you're worried about switching speed, or if you use CHR-RAM and don't need any banswitching. The limit is 128kb CHR no matter if you use 8k more or 4k mode.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


